   "y": 516,
   "width": 660,
   "height": 140,
   "text": "branding + brand research (org-admin only)\norg settings\nknowledge base: vault + lexical index (org-partitioned)\nintegration credentials (e.g. M365 workspace token)\nanonymisation deny-lists (CRUD /api/v1/org/deny-list, org-admin, metadata-only)\norg-shared memories + artifacts\nautomations, triggers + their runs\nRegisto read surface (org activity, metadata only) - now covers login + build + CRUD writes (F3)",
