  {
   "type": "text",
   "id": "vis_body",
   "x": 76,
   "y": 730,
   "width": 1350,
   "height": 52,
   "text": "private -> owner only; invisible to org admins too (existence appears in Registo metadata, never content).\norg-shared -> visible + editable by org members (git version snapshots + restore + Registo cover every mutation).\ncross-org access is impossible by construction (structural scoping) - the cross-org adversarial suite proves it.",
   "originalText": "private -> owner only; invisible to org admins too (existence appears in Registo metadata, never content).\norg-shared -> visible + editable by org members (git version snapshots + restore + Registo cover every mutation).\ncross-org access is impossible by construction (structural scoping) - the cross-org adversarial suite proves it.",
